OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,8,FGlenton
OL,10,FThe price of oil soared to more than
OL,11,F$120 a barrel for the first time in
OL,12,Ffour years as the sector continues to
OL,13,Fbe shaken by the conflict in the
OL,14,FMiddle East.
OL,16,FThe FTSE 100, which tracks the value
OL,17,Fof the 100 wealthiest companies in the
OL,18,FUK listed on the London Stock
OL,19,FExchange, also plunged as higher oil
OL,20,Fprices caused uncertainty for
OL,21,Finvestors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FBut what is the tangible impact of
OL,8,Fthose numbers on everyday indicators
OL,9,Fsuch as food prices, energy bills,
OL,10,Fmortgages, travel and pensions? ITV
OL,11,FNews explains.
OL,13,FPetrol prices
OL,15,FCrude oil is a key benchmark for how
OL,16,Fmuch oil costs across Europe, Africa,
OL,17,Fand the Middle East. A sharp spike in
OL,18,Fhow much it costs pushes up the price
OL,19,Fof wholesale oil, which has a knock-on
OL,20,Feffect at the petrol pump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
