CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FThe RAC said the average price of a
OL,8,Flitre of petrol at UK forecourts was
OL,9,F137.5p on Sunday after rising nearly
OL,10,F5p since February 28, when the
OL,11,Fconflict in the Middle East started.
OL,13,FAverage diesel prices were up almost
OL,14,F9p over the same period to 151p.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
