OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FIf the price of oil continues to
OL,8,Fincrease - Qatar's finance minister
OL,9,Fhas suggested oil prices could reach
OL,10,F$150 a barrel - the cost of petrol
OL,11,Fwill likely follow suit.
OL,13,FAnalysis by the Energy and Climate
OL,14,FIntelligence Unit (ECIU) suggests that
OL,15,Fwould push petrol prices up to at
OL,16,Fleast #1.90 a litre, making costs
OL,17,Fsimilar to those in 2022 following
OL,18,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
