OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FOne factor affecting the price is the
OL,8,Ffact that a fifth of the world's oil
OL,9,Ftravels through the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,10,Fa narrow passage that connects the
OL,11,FPersian Gulf to the Gulf of Oman.
OL,13,FIran controls the entire northern
OL,14,Fside, and it has carried out attacks
OL,15,Fon ships passing through, which has
OL,16,Fled to shipping companies suspending
OL,17,Foperations in the area.
OL,19,FEnergy bills
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
