OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FEnergy prices in the UK are also
OL,8,Flikely to be impacted by the surge in
OL,9,Fwholesale global prices.
OL,11,FQatar's state-backed energy company
OL,12,FQatarEnergy halted its production of
OL,13,Fliquified natural gas (LNG) - the
OL,14,Fproduct of changing natural gas into
OL,15,Fliquid so that it can be transported
OL,16,Facross the world before it is
OL,17,Freliquefied and used by homes and
OL,18,Fbusinesses - on March 2 because of
OL,19,Fattacks on its facilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
