OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FQatarEnergy is the world's second-
OL,8,Flargest exporter of LNG, so any
OL,9,Fdisruption to its gas deliveries has
OL,10,Fan international impact.
OL,12,FWhether you see a change in your
OL,13,Fenergy bills, and by how much, will
OL,14,Fdepend on your energy supplier and
OL,15,Fyour specific tariff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
