OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FOctopus Energy, for example, has said
OL,8,Fcustomers on its flexible rate won't
OL,9,Ffeel the impact of the latest market
OL,10,Fspikes until July at the earliest,
OL,11,Fwhile anybody on a fixed tariff will
OL,12,Fcontinue to have that same fixed rate
OL,13,Funtil the end of that contract.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
