CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FRegulator Ofgem announced a 7% drop in
OL,8,Fthe energy price cap after Chancellor
OL,9,FRachel Reeves scrapped the Energy
OL,10,FCompany Obligation (Eco) scheme in her
OL,11,FNovember Budget.
OL,13,FFood prices
OL,15,FEnergy and petrol prices also make a
OL,16,Fdifference to how much our food costs,
OL,17,Ffrom the price of fertilizing crops
OL,18,Fand manufacturing to the cost of
OL,19,Ftransporting products to supermarket
OL,20,Fshelves.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
