OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FThe ongoing war in Ukraine had a huge
OL,8,Fimpact on global food supplies because
OL,9,Fthe country accounted for around 10%
OL,10,Fof global wheat exports and 12% of
OL,11,Fcorn and barley exports before
OL,12,FRussia's invasion.
OL,14,FThe UK is far less dependent on the
OL,15,FMiddle East for direct food supplies,
OL,16,Fso it is more likely to be
OL,17,Finterruptions to energy and oil prices
OL,18,Fthat have a domino effect on
OL,19,Fsupermarket prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FAround 20-30% of global fertilizer
OL,8,Fexports travel through the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz, according to global
OL,10,Findependent provider of energy and
OL,11,Fcommodity market intelligence Argus,
OL,12,Fso continued disruption there will
OL,13,Falso affect fertilizer distribution
OL,14,Fand crop production, which could
OL,15,Fimpact food prices further down the
OL,16,Fline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
