OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FGlobal stock markets have dipped in
OL,8,Fthe last week, and that can have an
OL,9,Fimpact on pensions as a sizeable
OL,10,Fportion of most people's retirement
OL,11,Ffunds are invested in the stock market.
OL,13,FBut most workplace and personal
OL,14,Fpensions are spread across lots of
OL,15,Fdifferent types of investments so that
OL,16,Fthe funds can weather shocks - such as
OL,17,Fglobal conflicts - more easily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FAnd while stock markets saw a downward
OL,8,Ftrend, and precious metal prices
OL,9,Fdipped, oil and gas producers and
OL,10,Fdefensive stocks have historically
OL,11,Ftended to perform well in times of
OL,12,Fpolitical uncertainty, and pension
OL,13,Fproviders will have accounted for
OL,14,Fvarying amounts of volatility,
OL,15,Fdepending on what type of plan you
OL,16,Fhave.
OL,18,FWhile there may be short-term dips in
OL,19,Fa pension pot, they are typically
OL,20,Fdesigned for long-term growth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,F"If your pension has decades to grow,
OL,8,Fit will likely have time to recover
OL,9,Ffrom market dips or crashes i.e., when
OL,10,Fthe stock market falls more than 20%,
OL,11,Flike the 2008 global financial crash
OL,12,Fand more recently, the Covid-19
OL,13,Fpandemic," savings and investment
OL,14,Fplatform Moneybox advises on its
OL,15,Fwebsite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FAnd while heightened volatility can be
OL,8,F"uncomfortable", it's also a reminder
OL,9,Fof why a long-term perspective is
OL,10,Fimportant, Kate Marshall, lead
OL,11,Finvestment analyst at Hargreaves
OL,12,FLansdown, said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,F"Periods of heightened volatility can
OL,8,Fbe uncomfortable, but they're also a
OL,9,Freminder of why diversification and a
OL,10,Flong-term perspective matter. By
OL,11,Ffocusing on these fundamentals rather
OL,12,Fthan daily market movements, investors
OL,13,Fgive themselves a better chance of
OL,14,Fachieving smoother progress towards
OL,15,Ftheir financial goals."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
