OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FHSBC UK, NatWest, Nationwide Building
OL,8,FSociety, and Coventry Building Society
OL,9,Fare among the lenders who have pushed
OL,10,Fup some mortgage rates in the last
OL,11,Fcouple of days in response to what is
OL,12,Fhappening in the Middle East.
OL,14,FFinancial information website
OL,15,FMoneyfacts said it had seen several
OL,16,Fother lenders adjusting rates on
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,19,FIts figures also indicate that some
OL,20,Faverage rates on fixed mortgages have
OL,21,Fjumped over the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
