OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FThe average two-year fixed homeowner
OL,8,Fmortgage rate on the market on Monday
OL,9,Fmorning was 4.87%, up from 4.84% on
OL,10,FFriday. The average five-year fixed
OL,11,Fhomeowner mortgage rate on Monday
OL,12,Fmorning was 4.98%, rising from 4.96%
OL,13,Fon Friday.
OL,15,FGlobal conflict can cause mortgage
OL,16,Frates to increase because lenders lose
OL,17,Fconfidence in the stability of the
OL,18,Fmarkets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
