CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773072686
OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FLower interest rates by the Bank of
OL,8,FEngland allow banks to offer cheaper
OL,9,Fmortgage rates, and while the base
OL,10,Frate was set to fall this year,
OL,11,Finternational uncertainty can put a
OL,12,Fpause on rate cuts while the bank's
OL,13,Fmonetary policy committee waits to see
OL,14,Fhow global events will unfold.
OL,16,FBank of England Governor Andrew Bailey
OL,17,Fsaid in February he expected "to see
OL,18,Fquite a sharp drop in inflation over
OL,19,Fthe coming months" when the interest
OL,20,Frate was held at 3.75%, but global
OL,21,Fevents will likely alter that outlook.
