OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FInternational travel costs
OL,9,FJet fuel is predominantly made from
OL,10,Fcrude oil, so fluctuations in that
OL,11,Fmarket have a direct impact on the
OL,12,Faviation sector.
OL,14,FJet fuel typically makes up 25-30% of
OL,15,Fairline operating costs, according to
OL,16,Fthe International Air Transport
OL,17,FAssociation (IATA), so when prices
OL,18,Fspike, it can make a big difference to
OL,19,Fan airline's bottom line - and that
OL,20,Fcan affect how much they charge for
OL,21,Fplane tickets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
