OL,3,CFood prices, energy bills and
OL,4,Cpensions: What is the impact of the
OL,5,CIran war?
OL,7,FOn March 5, jet fuel prices hit a
OL,8,Frecord cost for a third consecutive
OL,9,Fday because of the conflict in Iran,
OL,10,Faccording to Argus.
OL,12,FWhile most airlines haven't said
OL,13,Foutright that tickets will get more
OL,14,Fexpensive, Wizz Air told Reuters it
OL,15,Fwould see a dip in profit because of
OL,16,Fwhat is happening in the Middle East,
OL,17,Fwhile United Airlines CEO Scott Kirby
OL,18,Ftold CNBC its financial results would
OL,19,Falso see a dent because of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/23
